<div class='center'><b>Alerts</b></div>
<div class="data_box3">
This page allows you to setup site monitoring and alerting.<p/>
<p></p>
Background information:
  <li>this application is designed to be deployed to multiple servers (typically two)
  <li><b>Peer</b> sites <b>monitor</b> each other, once every <b>three minutes</b>
  <li>if the <b>Peer</b> site is down for more than <b>15 minutes</b>, an <b>Alert email</b> is sent
  <li><b>Alert emails</b> continue to be sent every hour, as long as the <b>Peer</b> site is down
  <li><b>Notification emails</b> are sent after a site has been upgraded or restarted
  <li>Click here to learn more</li>
</div>
<div class="center">
  <b>Please don't change these settings unless you know what you are doing!!!</b>
</div>
<p/>
